%h2 Flexbox
%p Only supported in Gecko and Webkit browsers the flexible box is an alternative to the box model.
%blockquote
  %p The children of a box are laid out either horizontally or vertically, and unused space can be assigned to a particular child or distributed among the children by assignment of ‘flex’ to the children that should expand.
